Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:01.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,保持呼吸\N{\fs40}Keep breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:08.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用力\N{\fs40}And push.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,再来一次\N{\fs40}And again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我做不到\N{\fs40}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:24.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用力！\N{\fs40}Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:28.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,头出来了！\N{\fs40}The head!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是个男孩 公主殿下\N{\fs40}A boy, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:45.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,赞美圣母！\N{\fs40}Praise the Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:00.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,健康吗？\N{\fs40}Healthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,踢得像山羊一样有力 公主殿下\N{\fs40}Kicking like a goat, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:18.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主殿下……\N{\fs40}Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:23.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后要求把孩子带去见她……\N{\fs40}the Queen has requested that the child be brought to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在就要\N{\fs40}immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:28.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fs40}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我自己带他去\N{\fs40}I'll take him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:41.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您应该卧床休养 公主殿下——\N{\fs40}You should remain abed, Princess--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是 我是该躺着！帮我更衣\N{\fs40}Yes, I should! Help me dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,殿下……\N{\fs40}Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,换一下裙子？\N{\fs40}your dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主殿下？\N{\fs40}Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 它出来了 - 胎盘！\N{\fs40}-It's coming. -The afterbirth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是个男孩 我刚听说了\N{\fs40}A boy. I've just heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 干得好\N{\fs40}-Yes. -Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪儿？ - 她想看他\N{\fs40}-Where are you going? -She wants to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:02.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在？\N{\fs40}Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:05.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我跟你一起去\N{\fs40}I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我也觉得 - 让我抱着他\N{\fs40}-I should hope so. -Let me take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不行 她休想看我的笑话\N{\fs40}No, she'll get no such satisfaction from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 还是扶着我的胳膊吧\N{\fs40}Just take my arm, at the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:18.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,疼得特别厉害吗？\N{\fs40}Was it terribly painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:20.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七神啊\N{\fs40}Oh gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我曾被长枪刺穿过肩膀\N{\fs40}I took a lance through the shoulder once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我深表同情\N{\fs40}My deepest sympathies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:32.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主殿下…… 公主殿下……\N{\fs40}The Princess... The Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:35.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我真庆幸自己不是女人\N{\fs40}I am glad I am not a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:37.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 公主殿下…… - 大人……\N{\fs40}-My Princess... -My Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N{\fs40}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,怎么了？出什么事了？\N{\fs40}What is it? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,操\N{\fs40}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,走 快走！\N{\fs40}Walk. Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她到底想干嘛？\N{\fs40}What could she possibly want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:02.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我以为这事已经翻篇了\N{\fs40}I thought we were past this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主殿下 兰尼诺爵士 很荣幸\N{\fs40}Princess, Ser Laenor, it is a privilege
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,能成为第一批向您道喜的人\N{\fs40}to be amongst the first to congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:13.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 卡斯威大人\N{\fs40}Thank you, Lord Caswell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我能帮上您的忙\N{\fs40}If I may be of any service.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,总有这么一天的 大人\N{\fs40}The day may yet come, my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:28.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们这就回去 好吗？\N{\fs40}We are turning back, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她可以来找我们 对吧？\N{\fs40}She can come to us, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:34.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 除非你想把我扛下那该死的台阶\N{\fs40}No. Not unless you wish to carry me down those fucking stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这真荒唐\N{\fs40}This is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主殿下\N{\fs40}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:33.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉！你刚生完孩子 应该好好休息\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra! You should be resting after your labors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:37.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我相信这是您的真心话 陛下\N{\fs40}I have no doubt that you would prefer that, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:39.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你得坐下来\N{\fs40}You must sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,塔雅 给公主拿个靠垫来\N{\fs40}Talya, fetch a cushion for the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 没有这个必要 - 别犟了\N{\fs40}-There's no need. -Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们等下再谈\N{\fs40}We'll finish this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:57.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大早上的这是什么好消息\N{\fs40}What happy news this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:00.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,的确 陛下\N{\fs40}Indeed, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:01.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他人呢？\N{\fs40}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:05.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的外孙在哪儿？这儿呢\N{\fs40}Where is my grandson? There.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他在这呢\N{\fs40}There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好王子\N{\fs40}A fine Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,很结实\N{\fs40}Sturdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你会成为一名令人生畏的骑士\N{\fs40}You will make a fearsome knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的 你会的\N{\fs40}Yes, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,孩子取名字了吗？\N{\fs40}Does the babe have a name yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:24.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们还没谈——\N{\fs40}We haven't spoken--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,乔佛里\N{\fs40}Joffrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他叫乔佛里\N{\fs40}He'll be called Joffrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这名字对瓦列利安家族来说真是少见呢\N{\fs40}That's an unusual name for a Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:34.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他的鼻子真是像了他爸爸\N{\fs40}I do believe he has his father's nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不是吗？\N{\fs40}Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果您不介意的话 陛下\N{\fs40}If you don't mind, Your Grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:48.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您的女儿表现英勇 现在该休息了\N{\fs40}your daughter has exerted herself heroically and should rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:49.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是当然\N{\fs40}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs40}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 我的女儿\N{\fs40}Well done, my girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我真的希望分娩顺利\N{\fs40}I do hope the labor was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:12.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想我管产婆叫婊子来着\N{\fs40}I think I called the midwife a cunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,继续努力吧 兰尼诺爵士\N{\fs40}Do keep trying, Ser Laenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,迟早会有个长得像你的孩子\N{\fs40}Soon or late, you may get one who looks like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:44.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不觉得给我的孩子取名字之前最好问问我吗？\N{\fs40}You don't think to consult me before you name my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:46.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他是我们的孩子 不是吗？\N{\fs40}He's our child, is he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,咱俩之间可只有一个人流血了\N{\fs40}Only one of us is bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:53.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我对自己的家事应该是有发言权的吧\N{\fs40}I deserve some say in the affairs of my own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:56.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你最近可是对我们的家事没什么兴趣呢\N{\fs40}You haven't seemed so interested in our affairs of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:12.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然后他看见了一条可怕的巨龙！\N{\fs40}And he sees a big, scary dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,母亲……\N{\fs40}Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看\N{\fs40}look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们给娃娃选了一颗龙蛋\N{\fs40}We chose an egg for the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看上去真合适\N{\fs40}That looks like the perfect one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:34.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我让小路去选的 - 谢谢你 小杰\N{\fs40}-I let Luke choose. -Thank you, Jace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:37.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不是每天都有龙蛋能带出龙穴的 公主\N{\fs40}Not every day an egg leaves the Dragonpit, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:40.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以我护送孩子们过来\N{\fs40}I thought it best to escort the lads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:43.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺和我谢谢你 队长\N{\fs40}Laenor and I thank you, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,又是个男孩 我听说\N{\fs40}Another boy, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你将来成了骑士 得多优秀啊 嗯？\N{\fs40}What a fine knight you are going to make, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可以吗？\N{\fs40}Might I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哈尔温爵士希望见见乔佛里\N{\fs40}Ser Harwin wishes to be introduced to Joffrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs40}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:07.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,叫乔佛里 是吧？\N{\fs40}Joffrey, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,父亲 我可以抱抱乔佛里吗 拜托？\N{\fs40}Father, please may I hold Joffrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 不 不可以\N{\fs40}No, no. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们两个 回去龙穴\N{\fs40}Back to the Dragonpit for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:25.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 拜托！ - 趁他们还没派人找你们\N{\fs40}-Come on! -Before they send out a search party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:39.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在都城守备队队长面前睡得那么熟\N{\fs40}You're asleep in front of the Commander of the City Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,太不尊重人了\N{\fs40}Terrible lack of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:47.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恐怕这种傲慢无礼是家族传统吧\N{\fs40}A certain insolence runs in the family, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让沃马克斯乖乖听话 杰卡里斯王子\N{\fs40}Call Vermax to heel, Prince Jacaerys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:17.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,沃马克斯！\N{\fs40}Vermax!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:19.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,沃马克斯！\N{\fs40}Vermax!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:27.22,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Zaldrizo aoho syt aeksio sagon ao bevilza,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:28.85,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}darilaros nuhys--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你必须好好控制你的龙 我的小王子\N{\fs40}You must hold mastery over your dragon, my young Princes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:33.94,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}...hae Darilarot Aegot Vvsperzomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就像伊耿王子对阳炎那样\N{\fs40}As Prince Aegon has with Sunfyre.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:38.94,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Zijosy aot tetiri ozlettosy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:43.16,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}toli rybagon zirylo vindilza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一旦和你心灵相连 他们便会拒绝\N{\fs40}Once they're fully bound to you, they will refuse
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,其他任何人发出的指令\N{\fs40}to take instruction from any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我能说吗？\N{\fs40}Can I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.34,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,龙焰 沃马克斯！\N{\fs40}Dracarys, Vermax!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:26.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊蒙德 我们为你准备了一个惊喜\N{\fs40}Aemond, we have a surprise for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:29.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 是什么？ - 非常特别的东西\N{\fs40}-What is it? -Something very special.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,咱们就你没龙\N{\fs40}You're the only one of us without a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,确实\N{\fs40}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们感到很遗憾\N{\fs40}And we felt badly about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:40.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,于是为你找了一只\N{\fs40}so we found one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:43.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙？怎么可能？\N{\fs40}A dragon? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七神给予\N{\fs40}The gods provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:56.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 看哪 - 粉死神！\N{\fs40}-Behold-- -The Pink Dread!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一定要小心骑上她\N{\fs40}Be sure to mount her carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:02.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,第一次上天总是很难\N{\fs40}First flight's always rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:41.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这只有60节\N{\fs40}This one has 60 rings...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:44.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,每节有两对足\N{\fs40}and two pairs of legs on each.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,总共就是240\N{\fs40}That's 240.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:48.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs40}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:52.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,它有眼睛……\N{\fs40}It has eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:54.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然而……\N{\fs40}though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我觉得它看不见\N{\fs40}I don't believe it can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你觉得这是为什么呢？\N{\fs40}And why is that so, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这超出了我们的认知\N{\fs40}It is beyond our understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想你是对的 有些事情就是这样\N{\fs40}I suppose you're right. Some things just are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:17.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊蒙德\N{\fs40}Aemond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你干嘛了？ - 他又去了\N{\fs40}-What have you done? -He did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:21.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,警告过你多少次了\N{\fs40}After how many times you've been warned,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:23.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,非得让我把你锁在房间里吗？！\N{\fs40}must I have you confined to your chambers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 他们逼我这么做的！ - 说得好像你需要别人督促一样\N{\fs40}-They made me do it! -As if you needed encouragement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:27.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你对那些畜生的痴迷真让人难以置信\N{\fs40}Your obsession with those beasts goes beyond understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:28.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们给了我一头猪！\N{\fs40}They gave me a pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:30.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一头什么？\N{\fs40}A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们声称找了一条龙给我\N{\fs40}They said they found a dragon for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最后一节没长腿\N{\fs40}The last ring has no legs at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但那是一头猪\N{\fs40}But it was a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,总有一天你会有条龙\N{\fs40}You will have a dragon one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:42.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 他得闭上一只眼 - 我知道\N{\fs40}-He'll have to close an eye. -I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:44.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们全都在笑我\N{\fs40}They all laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:51.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,很明显 他们给猪身上装了翅膀 还有条尾巴\N{\fs40}They made wings for it, apparently, and a tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:53.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小家伙不该轻信他人\N{\fs40}The lad shouldn't have been so credulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:54.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他还是个孩子\N{\fs40}He's a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:57.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他以为他们碰巧遇上了条无主野龙\N{\fs40}He thought they'd happened upon some wild unnamed dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还把它引来龙穴？\N{\fs40}and lured it to the Dragonpit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:00.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是您的外孙干的好事\N{\fs40}Your grandsons are a menace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们比伊蒙德还小呢\N{\fs40}They're more children than he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:05.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们是野孩子 没什么可奇怪的\N{\fs40}They're savages. And it's not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:10.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你确定不是我们的伊耿撺掇的吗？\N{\fs40}Are you sure it wasn't our Aegon who put them up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们的龙蛋能孵化 简直是奇迹\N{\fs40}It's a wonder to me their eggs ever hatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 为什么这么说？ - 您明白为什么\N{\fs40}-And why is that? -You know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 恐怕我不明白 - 别装了！\N{\fs40}-I'm afraid I don't. -Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯\N{\fs40}Viserys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,艾德 我们今天下午继续\N{\fs40}We shall continue this afternoon, Eddard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我曾向您提过此事\N{\fs40}I have raised this matter before
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:43.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为您不让我说 所以我闭口不谈\N{\fs40}and you forbade me to speak of it, so I held my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:47.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那样的孩子 生一个是犯错\N{\fs40}To have one child like that is a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,生了三个就是侮辱\N{\fs40}to have three is an insult,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:53.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,侮辱了王座 您 和瓦列利安家族\N{\fs40}to the throne, to you, to House Velaryon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有您千辛万苦为她找到的对象\N{\fs40}and the match you battled so hard to make for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:58.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,更别提做人的体面了\N{\fs40}Not to mention decency itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:01.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我养过一匹黑色的母马\N{\fs40}I had a black mare once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:04.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,黑如渡鸦\N{\fs40}Black like a raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:06.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,突然有一天 她逃离了牧场\N{\fs40}One day, she escaped her pasture
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:09.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,附近的公马在她身上下了种\N{\fs40}and the neighboring stallion sired a foal on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:15.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公马是银白色的 宛如冬夜的月光\N{\fs40}The stallion was as silver as the moon on a winter's night
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:18.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,至于小马驹 它出生后\N{\fs40}and the foal, when it was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,却是栗色的\N{\fs40}chestnut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:25.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就像是你曾见过的最不起眼的棕马\N{\fs40}Just the most unremarkable brown horse you ever saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:30.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大自然的伟力神秘莫测\N{\fs40}Nature is a thing of mysterious works.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您怎么确信？\N{\fs40}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那匹银色公马\N{\fs40}The silver stallion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:43.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您怎么能确定就是他？\N{\fs40}How do you know it was him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,难道您亲眼见证了他们交配？\N{\fs40}Did you witness the act itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:53.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,由你随意的指控\N{\fs40}The consequences
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:56.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,导致的结果\N{\fs40}of an allegation like the one you toy at
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会非常严重\N{\fs40}would be dire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别再提此事了\N{\fs40}Do not speak of this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,难道是我失去理智了吗，科尔爵士？\N{\fs40}Have I lost my sanity, Ser Criston?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是我的感性让我误入歧途？\N{\fs40}Do my senses lead me astray?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:25.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是所有人都睡着了 做着同一个糊涂梦？\N{\fs40}Or is everyone else asleep, dreaming the same woolly dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:27.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有时候或许是这样的 王后陛下\N{\fs40}Sometimes seems so, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她不知羞耻地炫耀自己身为继承人的特权\N{\fs40}She flaunts the privilege of her inheritance without shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:34.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她指望着红堡里的每个人都否认真相\N{\fs40}She expects everyone in the Red Keep to deny the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,否认每一双眼睛明白看到的事实\N{\fs40}our eyes can all plainly see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 至于国王 她的父亲 - 他知情\N{\fs40}-And the King, her father-- -He knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:38.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他当然知道\N{\fs40}Of course, he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:40.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,至少曾经知道 可他说服了自己\N{\fs40}Or did once, but has convinced himself otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:42.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只会为她找借口\N{\fs40}He'll do naught but make excuses for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉公主厚颜无耻 冷酷无情\N{\fs40}The Princess Rhaenyra is brazen and relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:49.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就像蜘蛛 刺了猎物后吸食得干干净净\N{\fs40}A spider who stings and sucks her prey dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她就是个被宠坏了的贱逼\N{\fs40}A spoiled cunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是我僭越了 王后陛下 我道歉\N{\fs40}That was beneath me, Your Grace. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:05.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我必须相信\N{\fs40}I have to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:09.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,到头来 荣誉和体面会占上风\N{\fs40}that in the end, honor and decency will prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:13.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们需要坚持这一点 对待彼此也是这样\N{\fs40}We need to hew to that and to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:33.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谁出的主意？\N{\fs40}Whose idea was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:40.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那头猪\N{\fs40}The pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:41.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是你搞的吗？\N{\fs40}Was it your plot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:43.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不……\N{\fs40}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:47.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是小杰和……\N{\fs40}it was Jace and...uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:50.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就……就是他俩\N{\fs40}it...it was the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:52.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不确定是哪个\N{\fs40}I couldn't be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊蒙德是你弟弟\N{\fs40}Aemond is your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:55.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 呃 他也是个傻逼 - 我们是一家人\N{\fs40}-Well, he's a twat. -We are family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:58.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在家里可以铐着他 任由你随心所欲\N{\fs40}You may cuff him about as you wish at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:01.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但在外边 我们必须保护自己人\N{\fs40}but in the world, we must defend our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:02.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,挺好笑的\N{\fs40}It was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:05.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你认为雷妮拉的儿子们会永远被你玩弄于手掌心吗？\N{\fs40}Do you think Rhaenyra's sons will be your playthings forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:08.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就当前情况而言……\N{\fs40}As things stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:12.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉会登上王位 那时杰卡里斯·坦格利安就会是她的继承人\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra will ascend the throne and Jacaerys Targaryen will be her heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:16.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 所以呢？ - 你都快成年了\N{\fs40}-So? -You are nearly a man-grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:18.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,怎么眼界还这么短浅？\N{\fs40}How is it that you can be so shortsighted?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:22.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一旦雷妮拉掌权……\N{\fs40}If Rhaenyra comes into power...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:26.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你很有可能没命\N{\fs40}your very life could be forfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:28.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊蒙德同样如此\N{\fs40}Aemond's as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:32.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她会除掉对她继承大统的威胁\N{\fs40}She could move to cut off any challenge to her succession.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:34.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那我不威胁不就——\N{\fs40}Then I won't challenge--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:35.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你本身就是威胁！\N{\fs40}You are the challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:36.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你本身就是威胁 伊耿！\N{\fs40}You are the challenge, Aegon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:39.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只要你活着 还能喘气\N{\fs40}Simply by living and breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是国王的长子\N{\fs40}You are the King's firstborn son
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:49.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们知道 全天下人都知道\N{\fs40}and what they know, what everyone in the realm knows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:51.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在他们深入骨髓的观念里……\N{\fs40}in their blood and in their bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:55.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,总有一天 你会成为我们的王\N{\fs40}is that one day, you will be our King.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:05.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把衣服穿上\N{\fs40}Get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.65,0:24:03.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙焰！\N{\fs40}Dracarys!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.14,0:24:33.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,羊心非常美味\N{\fs40}The lamb hearts are excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.64,0:24:36.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们很幸运有好厨子 英主\N{\fs40}We are fortunate in our cook, Your Excellence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.47,0:24:37.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有一道梅子蛋糕没上来\N{\fs40}There's a plum-cake yet to be served,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.85,0:24:39.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,相信美味到我们会为碎屑打起来\N{\fs40}which will have us fighting over the crumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.90,0:24:41.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那在我们打起来之前……\N{\fs40}Then before we come to blows...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.44,0:24:47.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,先为征服者伊耿干一杯 敬您崇高的祖先\N{\fs40}a toast to Aegon the Conqueror, your exalted forebear,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.40,0:24:51.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他在流血世纪加入了我们对抗瓦兰提斯的大业\N{\fs40}who joined our cause against Volantis in the Century of Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.36,0:24:54.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他骑着巨龙贝勒里恩 飞到里斯来援助我们\N{\fs40}On the great dragon Balerion, he flew to our aid in Lys
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.70,0:24:58.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他烧毁了敌军的舰队 力挽狂澜\N{\fs40}and burned a fleet of enemy ships, thus turning the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.50,0:25:03.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 敬征服者伊耿 - 敬伊耿\N{\fs40}-Aegon the Conqueror. -To Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.34,0:25:08.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这就引出了另一个话题\N{\fs40}This brings me to some business.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.97,0:25:11.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我有个提议\N{\fs40}A proposal I wish to make
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.22,0:25:14.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,本着尊重我们双方传奇之盟的精神\N{\fs40}in the spirit of honoring our storied alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.14,0:25:16.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果想娶我们的哪个女儿 英主\N{\fs40}If your aim is to marry one of our daughters, Your Excellence,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.77,0:25:19.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您可以直说 不必给我们上历史课\N{\fs40}you might have said so and spared us the history lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.27,0:25:21.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs40}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.19,0:25:24.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不认为自己能配得上您的女儿 兰娜尔夫人\N{\fs40}I would not count myself so deserving, my Lady Laena.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.98,0:25:31.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是想为您在潘托斯提供一处永久住所\N{\fs40}I wish to offer you a permanent residence here in Pentos.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.45,0:25:33.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把这所宅子直接送给您\N{\fs40}This manse I would gift to you, outright,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.95,0:25:36.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,连带着农庄和土地\N{\fs40}along with its farms and lands,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.33,0:25:38.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有葡萄园和林地\N{\fs40}the vineyard and the wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.12,0:25:40.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,佃户每年都会缴纳赋税\N{\fs40}The tenants would pay their tributes annually
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.33,0:25:42.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给新的坦格利安领主\N{\fs40}to their new Targaryen lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.54,0:25:45.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您还可以在城市和港口自由出入\N{\fs40}You would have your freedom of the city and the harbor,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.13,0:25:47.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以彰显您的王家地位\N{\fs40}as befits your royal station.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.09,0:25:52.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我听着呢\N{\fs40}Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.55,0:25:55.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,里斯及其盟友卷土重来\N{\fs40}Lys and its allies rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.93,0:26:00.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,三城同盟会和多恩的科奥伦·马泰尔结盟\N{\fs40}The Triarchy has made common cause with Qoren Martell of Dorne.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.56,0:26:03.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们随时都有可能将目光转向北方\N{\fs40}At any moment, they may turn their sights north.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.69,0:26:06.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您家里有龙\N{\fs40}Your family has dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.19,0:26:09.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在有三只 或许以后还有第四只\N{\fs40}Three now, mayhaps four in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.03,0:26:14.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的目的是从三城同盟会的贪欲中保护潘托斯\N{\fs40}My aim is to protect Pentos from the lustful eye of the Triarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.95,0:26:18.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就像当年伊耿那样援助潘托斯……\N{\fs40}Aid Pentos in this, as Aegon once did...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.29,0:26:23.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的感激将盈满您的酒杯 多到盛不下\N{\fs40}and my gratitude will fill your cup and overflow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.54,0:26:25.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,英主 我们只是旅人\N{\fs40}Your Excellence, we are travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.92,0:26:28.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们在此地已经停留得够久了\N{\fs40}We've already extended our visit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.92,0:26:34.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您的馈赠非常慷慨\N{\fs40}It's a most generous offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.39,0:26:37.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们一定会加以考虑\N{\fs40}And one we will certainly entertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.88,0:27:10.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在考虑雷吉奥亲王的提议\N{\fs40}You are considering Prince Reggio's offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.50,0:27:12.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们在这儿生活得很好\N{\fs40}We have a good life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.59,0:27:16.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自由自在 还受到热情款待\N{\fs40}We're free to do as we please, welcomed and feted.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.09,0:27:18.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 作为永远的客人 - 正是\N{\fs40}-And eternally guests. -Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.47,0:27:21.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不需背负责任 无论是政治权谋\N{\fs40}We are without responsibility. The political scheming,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.51,0:27:24.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是反复无常的效忠对象或继承人\N{\fs40}the endless shifting of loyalties and succession
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.27,0:27:25.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这些事情都与我们无关\N{\fs40}is none of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.52,0:27:29.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 他们在利用我们 - 真是新鲜事 对吧？\N{\fs40}-They are using us. -It's refreshing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.98,0:27:32.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一笔简单的交易\N{\fs40}A simple transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.65,0:27:35.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们有龙 他们有金子\N{\fs40}We have dragons, they have gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.49,0:27:42.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们远不止于此 戴蒙\N{\fs40}We are more than this, Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.45,0:27:43.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们不是吟游诗人或者戏子\N{\fs40}We are not minstrels or mummers
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.87,0:27:45.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只为博取某位异国亲王的欢心而表演\N{\fs40}who play at the pleasure of an alien prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.54,0:27:47.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的身上流淌着古瓦雷利亚的血脉\N{\fs40}We are the blood of Old Valyria.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.96,0:27:50.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这儿不是我们的家\N{\fs40}We don't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.63,0:27:53.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦雷利亚早就没了 哪儿都不是我们的家\N{\fs40}Valyria is gone. We don't belong anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.89,0:28:03.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望把孩子生在我出生的地方 生在潮头岛上\N{\fs40}I want my child to be born where I was born, on Driftmark,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.64,0:28:04.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在我父亲大人的城堡里\N{\fs40}in my lord father's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.02,0:28:07.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望我的女儿在她们的故乡长大\N{\fs40}I want my daughters to be raised in their homeland
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.64,0:28:11.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,与亲人在一起 这是她们天生的权利\N{\fs40}with their family according to their birthright.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.78,0:28:17.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在我生命终结的时候 我希望作为驭龙者死去\N{\fs40}And at my end, I want to die a dragonrider's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.32,0:28:19.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而不是什么乡下的胖贵族\N{\fs40}Not that of some fat country lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.86,0:28:54.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,膝盖要放松\N{\fs40}Soften your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.40,0:28:56.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,脚步要轻盈\N{\fs40}Feet light.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.99,0:28:59.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,脚要轻手要重\N{\fs40}Keep your feet light and your hands heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.36,0:29:01.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就是这样啊 莱昂诺\N{\fs40}This is the stuff, Lyonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.99,0:29:05.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一起学习一起训练的小伙子们\N{\fs40}Lads that learn together, train together...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.49,0:29:08.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,打倒对方 又扶他起来\N{\fs40}knock each other down, pick each other up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.46,0:29:11.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然会形成一辈子的牵绊 不是吗\N{\fs40}They will certainly form a lifelong bond, wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.00,0:29:13.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,希望如此 陛下\N{\fs40}That is the hope, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.30,0:29:18.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别站得那么直 王子 会被打倒的\N{\fs40}Don't stand too upright, my Prince. You'll get knocked down.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.06,0:29:30.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿\N{\fs40}Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.85,0:29:34.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我赢得了第一场比赛 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}I've won my first bout, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.86,0:29:36.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的对手求饶了\N{\fs40}My opponent sues for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.61,0:29:40.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就给你来个新对手 我的稻草人大人\N{\fs40}You'll have a new opponent then, My Lord of the Straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.82,0:29:42.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来看看你能不能碰到我\N{\fs40}Let's see if you can touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.36,0:29:44.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你和你弟弟一起上\N{\fs40}You and your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.56,0:30:13.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还得努力啊\N{\fs40}You're gonna have to do better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.69,0:30:20.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,举起武器 孩子们\N{\fs40}Weapons up, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.78,0:30:22.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不要对敌人心慈手软\N{\fs40}Give your enemies no quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.41,0:30:27.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看样子你多给点关注的话\N{\fs40}It seems the younger boys could do better with a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.45,0:30:30.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这些小男孩们能练得更好 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}of your attention, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.41,0:30:33.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是在质疑我的教学方法吗 爵士？\N{\fs40}You question my method of instruction, ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.41,0:30:37.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只是建议你对所有学生都用上这些方法\N{\fs40}I merely suggest that method be applied to all your pupils.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.63,0:30:41.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs40}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.18,0:30:47.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杰卡里斯 过来\N{\fs40}Jacaerys, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.10,0:30:48.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你和伊耿对练\N{\fs40}You spar with Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.81,0:30:53.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,长子对长子\N{\fs40}Eldest son against eldest son.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.35,0:30:58.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 这不公平吧 - 我知道你从未见过\N{\fs40}-It's hardly a fair match. -I know you've never seen
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.36,0:30:59.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真正的战场 爵士 但是白刃相向之际\N{\fs40}true battle, ser, but when steel is drawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.02,0:31:01.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就没人能奢求公平了\N{\fs40}a fair match isn't something anyone should expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.74,0:31:05.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,举剑\N{\fs40}Blades up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.20,0:31:08.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,开打\N{\fs40}Engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.68,0:31:34.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 犯规 - 我来处理\N{\fs40}-Foul play. -I'll deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.23,0:31:39.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,扎稳脚跟 你重心低是个优势\N{\fs40}Plant your feet. You have a height advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.31,0:31:40.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,利用这一点 向他逼近……\N{\fs40}Use it. Advance on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.32,0:31:47.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,上啊！\N{\fs40}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.95,0:31:50.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,逼紧\N{\fs40}Close with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.99,0:31:53.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,逼他退后！逼紧！\N{\fs40}Press him backward! Close with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.79,0:31:55.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,持续进攻！用脚！\N{\fs40}Stay on the attack! Use your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.92,0:32:00.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不要让他爬起来\N{\fs40}Don't let him get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.67,0:32:03.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,保持进攻！\N{\fs40}Stay on the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.30,0:32:06.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,够了！\N{\fs40}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.26,0:32:10.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么敢碰我？ - 伊耿！\N{\fs40}-You dare put hands on me? -Aegon!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.97,0:32:12.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你失礼了 斯壮 这是王子殿下\N{\fs40}You forget yourself, Strong. That is the Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.93,0:32:14.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这就是你的教学吗 科尔？\N{\fs40}This is what you teach, Cole?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.10,0:32:18.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,残酷地……\N{\fs40}Cruelty...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.31,0:32:20.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对待更弱小的对手？\N{\fs40}to the weaker opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.48,0:32:27.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你对王子们训练的关心程度很不寻常啊 队长\N{\fs40}Your interest in the princeling's training is quite unusual, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.99,0:32:30.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大多数人只会以这样的热情\N{\fs40}Most men would only have that kind of devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.91,0:32:32.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去关心自己的表兄弟……\N{\fs40}toward a cousin...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.08,0:32:35.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或是兄弟……\N{\fs40}or a brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.20,0:32:37.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或是儿子\N{\fs40}or a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.26,0:32:55.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,后退！\N{\fs40}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.85,0:32:57.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你再说一遍！\N{\fs40}Say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.27,0:32:59.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,再说一遍！\N{\fs40}Say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.73,0:33:01.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我猜就是\N{\fs40}Thought as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.98,0:33:06.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,拿块浴巾给他洗澡\N{\fs40}Let him be bathed with a cloth,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.65,0:33:08.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然后让厨师\N{\fs40}and see to it the cook
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.44,0:33:10.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给你一杯清澈的好酒\N{\fs40}gives you a good, clear wine to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.82,0:33:13.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主殿下……\N{\fs40}Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.74,0:33:17.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,训练场上出了点事故\N{\fs40}there's been an incident in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.34,0:33:29.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这让我时刻感到羞耻\N{\fs40}It fills me with unrelenting shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:32.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以你就是为了这个？\N{\fs40}So that's what this is about then?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.09,0:33:33.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的耻辱\N{\fs40}Your shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.33,0:33:35.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的耻辱 哈尔温！\N{\fs40}Our shame, Harwin!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.60,0:33:37.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,整个斯壮家族的耻辱\N{\fs40}Shame on the whole of House Strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.31,0:33:40.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为我对那个让人无法忍受的科尔出手了？\N{\fs40}Because I laid my hands on that insufferable Cole,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.27,0:33:42.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 不就是个管家的儿子？ - 他现在是御林铁卫的骑士\N{\fs40}-the son of a steward? -He is a Knight of the Kingsguard now,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.73,0:33:44.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 是王家护卫 - 他攻击了杰卡里斯王子\N{\fs40}-a defender of the crown. -He assailed Prince Jacaerys,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.65,0:33:46.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王位未来的继承人\N{\fs40}the future heir to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.53,0:33:52.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而你使我们面临的指控\N{\fs40}You have laid us open to accusations
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.78,0:33:54.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是更加丑陋的背叛\N{\fs40}of an uglier treachery.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.62,0:33:56.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么背叛？\N{\fs40}And what treachery is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.29,0:34:01.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别跟我装傻 小子\N{\fs40}Don't play the fool with me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.04,0:34:06.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你和雷妮拉公主的亲密关系\N{\fs40}Your intimacy with the Princess Rhaenyra
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.29,0:34:09.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是会导致流放和死亡的罪行……\N{\fs40}is an offense that would mean exile and death...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.80,0:34:13.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不论是你 还是她 还是孩子们！\N{\fs40}for you, for her, for the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.51,0:34:17.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这只是谣言……\N{\fs40}It is rumor only...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.81,0:34:20.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是公主的对手散播的\N{\fs40}spun by the Princess's rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.27,0:34:22.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大家都有眼睛 孩子\N{\fs40}People have eyes, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.73,0:34:28.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然而国王陛下看起来似乎不愿意接受他的眼睛看见的东西\N{\fs40}Yet His Grace the King, it seems, will not accept what his eyes see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.78,0:34:33.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你和刽子手之间只隔着这么薄薄的一面盾\N{\fs40}This flimsy shield alone stands between you and the headsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.82,0:34:37.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个父亲对孩子执拗的盲目\N{\fs40}The willful blindness of a father towards his child.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.95,0:34:40.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,希望我的父亲也有同样的盲目\N{\fs40}I wish my father affected a similar blindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.50,0:34:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这么多年来难道我没有吗？\N{\fs40}Have I not these many years?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.41,0:34:45.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然而今天 你公开袭击\N{\fs40}And yet today, you publicly assaulted
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.67,0:34:48.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一位御林铁卫 为了维护你的——\N{\fs40}a Knight of the Kingsguard in the, in the defense of your--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.51,0:34:54.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您有您的荣誉 我也有我的\N{\fs40}You have your honor and I have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.85,0:35:04.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是镇痛的 公主\N{\fs40}To ease the pain, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.24,0:35:19.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 过两天就会好多了\N{\fs40}-Thank you. -You'll feel better in a day or two,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.99,0:35:21.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等奶水都回完了\N{\fs40}when the milk dries up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.22,0:35:42.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的妻子\N{\fs40}My dear wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.31,0:35:44.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主\N{\fs40}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.77,0:35:47.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我摔倒了\N{\fs40}I fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.44,0:35:52.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪了 - 和卡尔一起出去了 我没说吗？\N{\fs40}-Where have you been? -Out with Qarl. Didn't I mention it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.57,0:35:56.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你很痛吗？\N{\fs40}Are you in very much pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.95,0:35:57.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,奶水……\N{\fs40}The milk...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.20,0:36:01.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 会使胸部肿胀—— - 劳驾 卡尔爵士\N{\fs40}-swells the breasts-- -Would you mind, Ser Qarl?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.45,0:36:03.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想和丈夫说说话\N{\fs40}I would like to speak with my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.24,0:36:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然 公主殿下\N{\fs40}Of course, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.38,0:36:20.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,石阶列岛又要打仗了 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}War is afoot again in the Stepstones, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.35,0:36:25.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,三城同盟会和多恩结盟后如获新生\N{\fs40}The Triarchy takes new life from its alliance with Dorne.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.89,0:36:28.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们在拦截船只和货物\N{\fs40}They're waylaying ships and cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.52,0:36:32.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,卡尔在那里打过仗 他给我看——\N{\fs40}Qarl's been fighting there. He showed me a--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.44,0:36:39.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他给我看了一袋子核桃那么大的蓝宝石\N{\fs40}He showed me a sack of sapphires big as walnuts
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.32,0:36:41.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他从砍杀的海盗那里拿的\N{\fs40}he took from the pirate he slew.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.87,0:36:47.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这么多年了 这正是我需要的啊\N{\fs40}after all this time, this is just what I need,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.25,0:36:48.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一点点冒险\N{\fs40}a little adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.00,0:36:53.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一场酣畅淋漓的战斗使我重燃热血\N{\fs40}A good, honest battle to enliven my blood again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.71,0:36:56.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他说那里有个泰洛西将军\N{\fs40}He says there is a Tyroshi general there,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.38,0:36:58.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们说那是个巨人\N{\fs40}a giant, they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.22,0:37:02.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把胡子染成紫色 还穿着女人的罩袍\N{\fs40}who dyes his beard purple and wears women's frocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.68,0:37:08.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许过几个月……\N{\fs40}A few months, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.31,0:37:15.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就能回到大海上\N{\fs40}To be back at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.23,0:37:19.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？\N{\fs40}Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.07,0:37:21.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你知道发生了什么吗……\N{\fs40}Do you know what's happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.78,0:37:24.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当你在跳蚤窝畅饮麦酒\N{\fs40}while you've been guzzling all the ale in Flea Bottom?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.83,0:37:26.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或者天知道还在作什么的时候？\N{\fs40}Gods know what besides?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.58,0:37:29.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,黑暗的谣言在围猎我们 兰尼诺\N{\fs40}Dark rumors are hunting us, Laenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.96,0:37:32.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,啃噬我们的脚跟\N{\fs40}They nip at our heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.12,0:37:36.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,质疑我们儿子的出身\N{\fs40}Questions about our sons' parentage.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.92,0:37:41.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,卑鄙恶心的含沙射影\N{\fs40}Vile, disgusting insinuations.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.30,0:37:42.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,含沙射影 是吗？\N{\fs40}Insinuations, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.43,0:37:45.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们是我们的儿子\N{\fs40}They are our sons!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.47,0:37:47.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你和我的\N{\fs40}Yours and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.43,0:37:50.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们真正的父亲不会在此时抛下他们\N{\fs40}And their true father will not abandon them now
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.64,0:37:54.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去喝遍狭海 挥舞着佩剑\N{\fs40}to go carousing through the Narrow Sea, waggling his sword
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.27,0:37:56.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 跟水手眉目传情 - 我是个骑士……\N{\fs40}-and winking at his sailors. -I am a knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.86,0:38:01.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也是个战士\N{\fs40}and a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.11,0:38:06.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我忠实地扮演自己的角色\N{\fs40}And I have played my part here, faithfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.33,0:38:10.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,已经十年了\N{\fs40}for 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.50,0:38:14.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你们欠我—— - 什么都不欠你！\N{\fs40}-I am owed some-- -You are owed nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.54,0:38:20.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,十年来 你在宫廷里放纵\N{\fs40}For 10 years, you have indulged yourself at court,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.59,0:38:23.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,买最好的马\N{\fs40}bought the finest horses,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.13,0:38:25.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,喝最珍稀的酒\N{\fs40}drunk the rarest of wines,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.55,0:38:27.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,操最浪荡的男孩\N{\fs40}fucked the lustiest boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.35,0:38:30.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是我们的协议 我对这些没有意见\N{\fs40}This was our agreement. I have not begrudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.64,0:38:32.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是……\N{\fs40}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.40,0:38:38.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当风暴来袭时你不能抛弃岗位\N{\fs40}you do not desert your post when the storm lashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.73,0:38:43.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,明智的水手会趁风暴汇聚的时候逃走\N{\fs40}The wise sailor flees the storm as it gathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.75,0:38:55.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那好吧 我命令你\N{\fs40}Very well then. I command you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.46,0:38:59.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为公主和王储\N{\fs40}As your Princess and the heir to the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.71,0:39:01.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我命令你待在君临\N{\fs40}you are commanded to remain
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.01,0:39:04.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,待在我身边\N{\fs40}in King's Landing and at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.61,0:39:27.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,已经八年了 亲爱的\N{\fs40}It's been eight years, sweetling.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.16,0:39:32.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 有半数龙蛋是不会的 你知道吗？ - 不会什么？\N{\fs40}-Half of them never do, you know? -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.04,0:39:36.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,孵化\N{\fs40}Hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.13,0:39:40.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们会让我也留下么？\N{\fs40}Will they let me stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.09,0:39:43.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“他们”是谁？\N{\fs40}Will who let you stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.26,0:39:45.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,潘托斯亲王\N{\fs40}The Prince of Pentos.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.97,0:39:48.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没明白\N{\fs40}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.72,0:39:51.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他想要你和父亲……\N{\fs40}He wants you and father...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.10,0:39:54.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有贝妮拉……\N{\fs40}and Baela...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.10,0:39:56.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为你们有龙\N{\fs40}'cause you have dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.40,0:40:05.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和龙建立牵绊的方法不止一种\N{\fs40}There is more than one way to bind yourself to a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.19,0:40:09.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我直到15岁才有了龙\N{\fs40}I was without one until I was 15 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.87,0:40:14.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而现在我骑着瓦格哈尔 全世界最大的龙\N{\fs40}and now I ride Vhagar, the largest in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.41,0:40:19.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你要走的路会困难一些\N{\fs40}You have a harder road.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.33,0:40:21.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,贝妮拉的龙在她出生后不久就孵化了\N{\fs40}Baela's dragon was born to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.84,0:40:25.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但如果你想骑龙\N{\fs40}But if you wish to be a rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.51,0:40:28.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就要去自己争取\N{\fs40}you must claim that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.09,0:40:32.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你父亲也会这样跟你讲的\N{\fs40}Your father would tell you the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.60,0:40:35.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,父亲不理我\N{\fs40}Father ignores me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.94,0:40:43.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他已经尽力了\N{\fs40}He's doing his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.60,0:41:23.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺来信了\N{\fs40}Laenor has written.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.98,0:41:27.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉又生了个儿子\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra has delivered another son.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.57,0:41:31.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你哥哥有没有说这孩子\N{\fs40}Does your brother mention if this one
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.24,0:41:33.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也特别像都城守备队队长\N{\fs40}also bears a marked but entirely coincidental
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.87,0:41:36.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但纯属巧合？\N{\fs40}resemblance to the Commander of the City Watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.58,0:41:39.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他似乎略掉了这个细节\N{\fs40}He seems to have left that detail out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.92,0:41:45.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想我哥哥了 戴蒙\N{\fs40}I miss my brother, Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.55,0:41:49.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你应该也很思念哥哥吧\N{\fs40}As I think do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.93,0:41:53.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我思念维斯特洛的烈酒\N{\fs40}I miss Westerosi strongwine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.85,0:41:57.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,足以让人安详地淡忘好几个时辰\N{\fs40}It could be depended on for a few hours of peaceful oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.68,0:42:02.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这里的人只喝琥珀色的猫尿\N{\fs40}This amber shit that they drink here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.90,0:42:11.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你难道不想家么？\N{\fs40}Do you never long for home?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.03,0:42:13.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不想\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.53,0:42:16.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,-我才不信呢 -信不信随你咯\N{\fs40}-I don't believe you. -Believe what you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.20,0:42:20.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你赞美潘托斯的优点 却对它毫无兴趣\N{\fs40}You laud the virtues of Pentos, but you have no interest in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.37,0:42:22.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你要真喜欢潘托斯 早就去城里游历了 但结果呢\N{\fs40}If you did, you would venture into the city, but instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.00,0:42:26.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在图书室里打发时间 一遍遍地翻阅\N{\fs40}you spend your time here, in the library, reading accounts
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.54,0:42:31.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那些逝去的龙王的故事 还声称他们的遗产不会束缚你\N{\fs40}of the same dead dragonlords whose legacy you claim has no hold on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.51,0:42:33.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没想到还有人在时时刻刻监督我啊\N{\fs40}Didn't know I was being so minutely observed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.05,0:42:35.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你都不睡觉\N{\fs40}You do not sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.68,0:42:38.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,唔 你总这么守着我我哪睡得着呢\N{\fs40}Well, how can I with you haunting my every move?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.56,0:42:44.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道你的人生被辜负了\N{\fs40}Life has, I know, disappointed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.06,0:42:47.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可能我也辜负了你吧 不是你想要的妻子\N{\fs40}Perhaps, I too, am not the wife you would've wished for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.56,0:42:48.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰娜尔\N{\fs40}Laena.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.86,0:42:50.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我并不为此难过\N{\fs40}It does not pain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.65,0:42:53.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经放宽心态了\N{\fs40}I have made my peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.49,0:42:59.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你不该止步于此 戴蒙\N{\fs40}But you are more than this, Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.58,0:43:04.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我嫁的男人过去不会止步于此\N{\fs40}The man I married was more than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.30,0:43:14.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是布莱伍德大人的辩词\N{\fs40}It is Lord Blackwood's contention, therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.72,0:43:16.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他说是布拉肯家族趁着夜色\N{\fs40}that the Brackens moved the boundary stones
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.43,0:43:17.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,挪动了界石\N{\fs40}in the dead of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.85,0:43:20.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还把马放养在他的领地上吃草\N{\fs40}and put their horses to graze in his field.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.39,0:43:22.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那这事怎么不跟葛拉佛大人去讲？\N{\fs40}Why was this issue not brought before Lord Grover?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.06,0:43:26.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他已经虚弱到连为了块石头争吵这种事都摆不平了吗？\N{\fs40}Has he grown so feeble he cannot settle a quarrel over rocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.23,0:43:30.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我听说葛拉佛大人之子已经是奔流城有实无名的主人了\N{\fs40}I've heard tale that Lord Grover's son now rules Riverrun in all but name.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.69,0:43:34.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那他也是徒利家的人 就该管好徒利家的事\N{\fs40}Well, he is also a Tully and this remains a Tully problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.07,0:43:36.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我赞同\N{\fs40}I would agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.28,0:43:39.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 能进行下一个话题了吗 大人们 - 反正吧\N{\fs40}-If we may move on, my lords-- -And yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.78,0:43:41.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,布雷肯家族和布莱伍德家族\N{\fs40}the Brackens and the Blackwoods
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.33,0:43:43.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,随便什么理由都能跟对方争个你死我活\N{\fs40}will use any excuse to spill each other's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.62,0:43:49.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以这桩纠纷值得调查\N{\fs40}So this dispute bears looking into.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.00,0:43:51.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,肯定能找到了解实情的农民\N{\fs40}There will be countryfolk who know
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.59,0:43:53.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,知道祖辈是怎么划分地界的\N{\fs40}where the lines have been drawn for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.96,0:43:55.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是好办法\N{\fs40}That is easy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.43,0:43:57.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说得是呢\N{\fs40}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.14,0:44:01.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,泰兰大人\N{\fs40}Ser Tyland.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.02,0:44:04.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们需要处理\N{\fs40}We should address
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.81,0:44:07.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,石阶列岛的最新局势 大人们\N{\fs40}the latest developments in the Stepstones, my lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.73,0:44:10.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那地方的破事什么时候是个头？\N{\fs40}Will we ever be shut of that blasted place?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.52,0:44:12.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要我说呢 是布莱伍德家\N{\fs40}If you ask me, I think the Blackwoods have
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.40,0:44:13.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在这件事上更占理\N{\fs40}the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.56,0:44:14.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,服了\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.05,0:44:16.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们已经在说石阶列岛的问题了 毕斯柏里大人\N{\fs40}We've moved on to the Stepstones, Lord Beesbury.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.45,0:44:19.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,三女儿王国和多恩缔结了新的联盟\N{\fs40}And the Triarchy's new alliance with Dorne.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.99,0:44:22.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我原本希望咱们和阳戟城的沟通\N{\fs40}I was hoping our negotiations with Sunspear
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.53,0:44:24.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可以劝服多恩人理智行动\N{\fs40}might persuade them to see reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.54,0:44:28.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,指望马泰尔家族 必然会失望\N{\fs40}To trust a Martell is to be disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.79,0:44:31.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且我很好奇 咱们的戴蒙王子去哪了？\N{\fs40}And where, I wonder, is our Prince Daemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.38,0:44:33.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是我该按他自封的头衔叫他戴蒙王呢\N{\fs40}Or I suppose I should call him King, as he styled himself
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.92,0:44:36.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当时他在那里打赢了一场仗 就那一次\N{\fs40}when he won a battle there... once.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.63,0:44:39.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是十年前的事了 此后他就留着那里毫不设防\N{\fs40}That was a decade ago and he has since left the region undefended.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.47,0:44:41.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是我们留着那里毫不设防\N{\fs40}We have left it undefended.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.26,0:44:44.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们本该修筑防御工事\N{\fs40}There should've been fortifications built,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.31,0:44:46.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,望塔 舰队\N{\fs40}watchtowers, a fleet of ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.23,0:44:48.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有驻守士兵 才能守住它\N{\fs40}a garrison of soldiers sent to hold our ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.02,0:44:50.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们负担不起\N{\fs40}We cannot afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.48,0:44:55.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国库是很大 但终有上限\N{\fs40}Our coffers are great, but not infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.49,0:44:58.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们必须考虑臣民付出的代价\N{\fs40}We must consider the cost to our subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.53,0:45:01.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我非常赞同 - 战争的代价更大\N{\fs40}-I must agree. -The cost of war is greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.95,0:45:08.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我们一直忽视 现在过去的怪兽又冒头了\N{\fs40}But we have been lax and the old monster now lifts its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.42,0:45:14.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今天就到此为止吧\N{\fs40}Let us be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.92,0:45:17.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs40}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.76,0:45:22.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等下\N{\fs40}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.68,0:45:25.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我有话想说\N{\fs40}I wish to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.56,0:45:27.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大家就坐\N{\fs40}Be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.03,0:45:39.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我注意到……\N{\fs40}I have felt the...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.16,0:45:42.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们两家……\N{\fs40}strife...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.41,0:45:45.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最近有一些不合 王后陛下\N{\fs40}between our families of late, my Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.45,0:45:52.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我方对您的家人有什么冒犯 我向您道歉\N{\fs40}And for any offense given by mine, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.38,0:45:56.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我们本来是一家人\N{\fs40}But we are one house.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.63,0:46:00.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,更早之前\N{\fs40}And long before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.22,0:46:01.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们还曾是密友\N{\fs40}we were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.85,0:46:10.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的儿子杰卡里斯会从我这里继承铁王座\N{\fs40}My son Jacaerys will inherit the Iron Throne after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.60,0:46:13.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因此我提议让他和您的女儿海伦娜订亲\N{\fs40}I propose we betroth him to your daughter, Helaena.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.15,0:46:17.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,彼此结盟……\N{\fs40}Ally ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.77,0:46:19.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,永固统治\N{\fs40}once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.24,0:46:21.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让他们一道统治吧\N{\fs40}Let them rule together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.03,0:46:24.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,非常明智的提议\N{\fs40}A most judicious proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.08,0:46:32.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,另外 如果叙拉克丝还能再产一窝龙蛋\N{\fs40}Additionally, if Syrax brings forth another clutch of eggs,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.71,0:46:35.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您的儿子伊蒙德可以从中自行挑选\N{\fs40}your son Aemond will have his choice of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.42,0:46:38.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以示我方的友善\N{\fs40}a symbol of our goodwill.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.05,0:46:43.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.27,0:46:53.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,啊七层地狱啊 呃\N{\fs40}Oh, Seven Hells. Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.15,0:46:57.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好女儿……\N{\fs40}My dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.86,0:47:00.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙蛋是件慷慨的赠礼\N{\fs40}a dragon's egg is a handsome gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.90,0:47:05.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王和我感谢你的提议 我们会认真考虑的\N{\fs40}The King and I thank you for your offer and we will consider it duly.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.57,0:47:07.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你该休息了 夫君\N{\fs40}You must rest now, husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.79,0:47:12.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs40}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.50,0:47:22.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,狐狸被猎狗追到墙角时自然会甜言蜜语\N{\fs40}How sweetly the fox speaks when it's been cornered by the hounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.38,0:47:25.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 她是真心的 - 她是真急了\N{\fs40}-She is sincere. -She is desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.51,0:47:27.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,觉得自己的立足之地越来越小\N{\fs40}She feels the earth washing away beneath her feet
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.80,0:47:30.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在居然指望我们无视她的过错\N{\fs40}and now she expects us to ignore her transgressions
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.22,0:47:33.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我把唯一的女儿嫁给她那……\N{\fs40}and for me to marry my only daughter to one of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.56,0:47:35.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,相貌平平的儿子\N{\fs40}plain-featured sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.39,0:47:37.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这个提议很好 我的王后\N{\fs40}The proposal is a good one, my Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.06,0:47:40.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们是一家人\N{\fs40}We're a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.73,0:47:43.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就不要孩子气地争吵下去了\N{\fs40}Let us put aside these childish quarrels.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.15,0:47:45.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,联手才能更加强势\N{\fs40}Join hands and be stronger for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.70,0:47:48.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就如您所愿吧 夫君……\N{\fs40}You may do as you wish, husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.70,0:47:52.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等我在坟墓里凉透了 您就自行安排\N{\fs40}when I am cold in my grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.91,0:47:53.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森\N{\fs40}Alicent.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.91,0:47:56.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森！\N{\fs40}Alicent!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.61,0:48:22.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不用给我盖毯子——\N{\fs40}I do not need the blanket--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.11,0:48:27.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,首相求见 陛下\N{\fs40}The Hand, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.36,0:48:31.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 国王要休息 - 我可以见他\N{\fs40}-The King is resting. -I will see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.53,0:48:33.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坐起来点\N{\fs40}Lean forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.17,0:48:43.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,烦心事真是一个接一个啊 莱昂诺\N{\fs40}I'm being endlessly fussed over, Lyonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.71,0:48:47.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没人来厕所找我 真是奇迹\N{\fs40}It's a wonder I can visit the privy alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.09,0:48:49.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,抱歉 陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.26,0:48:52.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你过来又是有什么事 莱昂诺大人？\N{\fs40}What might this errand be about, Lord Lyonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.22,0:48:56.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 我认为……\N{\fs40}Your Grace, I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.14,0:49:01.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是来向您请辞国王之手一职的\N{\fs40}I have come to resign my position as Hand of the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.36,0:49:05.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今早院子里的插曲\N{\fs40}The episode in the yard this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.11,0:49:08.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,犬子哈尔温实在有失体面\N{\fs40}My son Harwin has disgraced himself
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.24,0:49:11.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用不了多久君临所有渔妇就都要嚼舌根了\N{\fs40}and every fishwife in King's Landing will soon be telling the tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.28,0:49:15.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,确实 年轻的哈尔温这般发火很不得体\N{\fs40}Young Harwin's outburst was unfortunate, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.58,0:49:17.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但他已经被都城守备队开除\N{\fs40}But he's been expelled from the City Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.33,0:49:18.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这个处罚已经足够了吧\N{\fs40}That seems punishment enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.79,0:49:21.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯 陛下 但并不足够\N{\fs40}Forgive me, Your Grace, it is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.30,0:49:32.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是我多年的忠臣\N{\fs40}You have served me faithfully for many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.55,0:49:33.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,首相也当了十年了\N{\fs40}10 as Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.39,0:49:39.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的意见一直明智无私\N{\fs40}Your advice has been sage, unmarked by self-interest...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.27,0:49:42.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可谓鹤立鸡群\N{\fs40}which stands in contrast to all others.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.31,0:49:45.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下过奖了……\N{\fs40}You speak kind words...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.23,0:49:49.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但现在阴影笼罩着我的家族\N{\fs40}but there is a shadow over my house
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.28,0:49:51.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,并且日渐昏暗\N{\fs40}and it grows ever darker.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.57,0:49:54.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我无法再正直地侍奉您\N{\fs40}I can no longer serve you with integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.62,0:49:57.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么阴影？\N{\fs40}What is this shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.58,0:50:00.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果它投下了这么深的阴影 那就明说吧\N{\fs40}Name it, if it casts such a gloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.04,0:50:05.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没错 我们必须听您明明白白地说出缘由\N{\fs40}Yes, we must have your reasoning in plain language.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.76,0:50:14.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不能说\N{\fs40}I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.81,0:50:18.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那我就不能同意你辞职\N{\fs40}Then I cannot accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.47,0:50:20.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 亲爱的丈夫—— - 我说了不行！\N{\fs40}- My dear husband-- - I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.81,0:50:24.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 如果您坚持的话 国王陛下 - 我坚持\N{\fs40}- If you insist, my King. - I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.36,0:50:27.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你将继续侍奉国王\N{\fs40}You will continue in your service to the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.07,0:50:32.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那我请求暂时离开 把我的儿子从宫中带走\N{\fs40}I would then ask leave to take my son from court
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.36,0:50:35.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,护送他回到赫伦堡的家里\N{\fs40}and escort him back to the family seat at Harrenhal.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.37,0:50:37.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他是我的继承人\N{\fs40}He is my heir
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.45,0:50:39.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有朝一日也将成为赫伦堡伯爵\N{\fs40}and will be lord of Harren's castle one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.33,0:50:41.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是时候让他担起这份责任了\N{\fs40}It is time he assumed his duties there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.04,0:50:45.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs40}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.94,0:51:08.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不打算帮我一下吗？\N{\fs40}Aren't you gonna help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.40,0:51:51.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后陛下 我先擅自开始了 没有等您\N{\fs40}I took the liberty of beginning without you, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.32,0:51:54.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让这么美味的派冷掉似乎是一种罪\N{\fs40}It seemed a sin to let such a pie grow cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.15,0:51:57.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,明智的做法 拉里斯大人\N{\fs40}You did wisely, Lord Larys.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.11,0:51:59.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过你肯定没这么担心过酒\N{\fs40}Though you had no such worry about the wine, surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.78,0:52:02.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,吃肉不喝酒也是一种罪\N{\fs40}Meat without wine is also a sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.29,0:52:10.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把红堡中发生的一切告知您是我的责任\N{\fs40}It's been my duty to tell you of happenings about the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.00,0:52:13.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过今晚的事您先知道了 我还不知道\N{\fs40}but tonight you know, and I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.88,0:52:17.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王面见了我的父亲\N{\fs40}The King had an audience with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.72,0:52:19.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他试图辞去职务\N{\fs40}He attempted to resign his post.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.35,0:52:21.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想也是\N{\fs40}I thought as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.93,0:52:26.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他那荣誉感一直是挂在他高贵脖颈上的重担\N{\fs40}His honor's always been a millstone about his esteemed neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.73,0:52:30.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有意思的是 您说他“试图”辞职？\N{\fs40}Interesting you said "attempted"?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.77,0:52:32.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的国王夫君拒绝接受\N{\fs40}My lord husband refused to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.03,0:52:37.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那看来他没能坦白我哥哥的……失德\N{\fs40}Then he fell short of confessing my brother's... transgressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.07,0:52:40.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你哥哥在院子里的情绪爆发\N{\fs40}With his eruption in the yard, your brother
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.37,0:52:42.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就已经供认了事情的真相\N{\fs40}all but confessed the truth himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.58,0:52:44.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真相的滋味可不止一种 王后陛下\N{\fs40}Truth has many flavors, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.87,0:52:48.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您难道期望着国王流放他亲爱的女儿\N{\fs40}Do you expect the King to doom his dear daughter to exile,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.62,0:52:50.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,甚至——\N{\fs40}or even--
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.04,0:52:53.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,塔雅 现在不是时候\N{\fs40}Talya, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.55,0:53:04.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是国王执拗的盲目\N{\fs40}It's a willful blindness, the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.22,0:53:05.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想 您肯定也有同样的苦恼\N{\fs40}I mean, you'd surely suffer the same affliction,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.89,0:53:07.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 如果碰到这种情况  - 我不会\N{\fs40}- if it came to it. - I would not.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.73,0:53:12.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,莱昂诺大人即将护送哈尔温爵士返回赫伦堡\N{\fs40}Lord Lyonel is to escort Ser Harwin back to Harrenhal
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.69,0:53:16.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,监管自己的族堡 同时继续担任首相\N{\fs40}to watch over his seat whilst he continues to serve as Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.69,0:53:21.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是首相已经被他儿子的行为危害\N{\fs40}But the Hand is compromised by the acts of his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.49,0:53:26.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我父亲已经无法向国王给出不偏不倚的建议\N{\fs40}My father cannot give unbiased counsel to the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.54,0:53:29.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就是现在这种时候让我最愤恨我父亲不在这里\N{\fs40}It is now that I most rue the absence of my own father.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.92,0:53:31.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他会毫不犹豫地告诉国王真相\N{\fs40}He wouldn't hesitate to speak the truth to the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.88,0:53:33.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,假如奥托·海塔尔还是首相——\N{\fs40}If Otto Hightower were still Hand--
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.50,0:53:35.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后陛下 您无法确定您的父亲\N{\fs40}You cannot say, my Queen, that your father would be
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.00,0:53:37.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在这件事上会不偏不倚\N{\fs40}impartial in this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.63,0:53:39.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 但他会偏向我！\N{\fs40}No, but he would be partial to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.27,0:53:52.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,整个君临城里 就没有人站在我这边吗？\N{\fs40}In all of King's Landing, is there no one to take my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.42,0:54:21.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我面前这是一群大英雄啊\N{\fs40}What a collection of heroes I have before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.60,0:54:27.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个杀人犯……\N{\fs40}A murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.93,0:54:29.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个变态……\N{\fs40}a deviant...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.52,0:54:32.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有一个王国的叛徒\N{\fs40}a traitor to the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.23,0:54:37.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,犯了这些罪 你们已经被判了绞刑\N{\fs40}For your crimes, you've been sentenced to death by hanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.40,0:54:41.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你想要我们怎样？\N{\fs40}What do you want with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.53,0:54:47.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我打算给你们仁慈……\N{\fs40}I am prepared to offer you mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.16,0:54:52.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你们愿意付出一点代价的话\N{\fs40}if you're prepared to pay a little price.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.27,0:55:17.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用力 夫人\N{\fs40}Push, my Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.02,0:55:19.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用力！用力！\N{\fs40}Push! Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.98,0:55:21.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用力！\N{\fs40}Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.65,0:55:25.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 您一定要用力！ - 用力！\N{\fs40}- You must push! - Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.24,0:55:29.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,必须现在就出来！\N{\fs40}It needs to come now!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.58,0:55:30.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用力！\N{\fs40}Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.83,0:55:34.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用力！\N{\fs40}Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.17,0:55:37.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您现在必须用力 夫人！\N{\fs40}You must push now, my Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.42,0:55:39.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用力！\N{\fs40}Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.19,0:56:00.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经尽我所能了\N{\fs40}I've reached the limit of my art.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.07,0:56:03.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,孩子还是出不来\N{\fs40}The child will not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.45,0:56:08.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我勇敢的女孩啊\N{\fs40}My brave girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.91,0:56:15.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 王子殿下\N{\fs40}I am very sorry, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.29,0:56:19.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们还可以试着用刀……\N{\fs40}We could lay open the womb...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.29,0:56:22.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,打开子宫\N{\fs40}try to remove the infant
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.59,0:56:23.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,取出婴儿\N{\fs40}by way of the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.47,0:56:28.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我无法保证它能活下来\N{\fs40}But I cannot say for a surety whether it lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.59,0:56:30.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,母亲能活下来吗？\N{\fs40}Would the mother survive it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.39,0:56:33.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不能\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.38,0:57:07.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦格哈尔 龙焰\N{\fs40}Vhagar, dracarys.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.93,0:57:13.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙焰！\N{\fs40}Dracarys!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.89,0:57:17.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙焰！\N{\fs40}Dracarys!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.77,0:57:23.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙焰\N{\fs40}Dracarys.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.15,0:57:26.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙焰！\N{\fs40}Dracarys!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.28,0:57:29.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙焰\N{\fs40}Dracarys.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.43,0:57:51.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰娜尔！\N{\fs40}Laena!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.57,0:58:16.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对你们的母亲好一些 小子们\N{\fs40}Be good to your mother, lads.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.83,0:58:18.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我有空就去看你们\N{\fs40}I'll visit when I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.92,0:58:23.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过可能得过些日子了\N{\fs40}But that may be some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.25,0:58:28.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小杰\N{\fs40}Jace.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.30,0:58:36.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会回来的……\N{\fs40}I will return...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.39,0:58:40.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fs40}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.66,0:58:59.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,再见面时 我就是个陌生人了\N{\fs40}I will be a stranger when we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.68,0:59:17.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主殿下\N{\fs40}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.91,0:59:42.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们可以用渡鸦传书\N{\fs40}We will exchange letters by raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.70,0:59:46.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 是不是很有意思？ - 哈尔温·斯壮是我父亲吗？\N{\fs40}- Won't that be fun? - Is Harwin Strong my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.50,0:59:52.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是私生子吗？\N{\fs40}Am I a bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.72,0:59:58.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是坦格利安族人\N{\fs40}You are a Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.35,1:00:01.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这才是唯一重要的事\N{\fs40}That's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.58,1:00:27.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,借一步说话？\N{\fs40}A word?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.46,1:00:35.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看来他已经走了\N{\fs40}I take it he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.34,1:00:40.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们不在这里待了 准备走吧\N{\fs40}We're finished here. We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.06,1:00:45.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你的提议呢？小杰和海伦娜的事？\N{\fs40}What of your offer? Jace and Helaena?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.02,1:00:47.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的形象已经被破坏了……\N{\fs40}I have been undermined...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.64,1:00:51.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经成了笑话 他们都在走廊里议论我\N{\fs40}and made a spectacle. They whisper about me in the corridors.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.94,1:00:54.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那好 随他们吧\N{\fs40}Well, I leave them to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.28,1:00:59.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那 回龙石岛吗？\N{\fs40}To Dragonstone then?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.49,1:01:02.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们早就该离开了\N{\fs40}We should've left years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.00,1:01:09.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的位子怎么办？\N{\fs40}What of your position?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.87,1:01:12.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你一直说如果你不在宫中\N{\fs40}You've always said if you were absent from court,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.21,1:01:15.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她就会在你父亲耳边进尽谗言\N{\fs40}she would pour her honey in your father's ear.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.88,1:01:19.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,明智的水手会趁风暴汇聚的时候逃走\N{\fs40}The wise sailor flees the storm as it gathers.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.89,1:01:22.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺……\N{\fs40}Laenor...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.22,1:01:25.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,带上他吧\N{\fs40}bring him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.52,1:01:29.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们需要每一把能使唤的剑\N{\fs40}We'll need every sword we can muster.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.18,1:02:49.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,着火了！我要烧死了！\N{\fs40}Fire! I will burn!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.68,1:02:52.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哈尔温！哈尔温！\N{\fs40}Harwin! Harwin!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.83,1:03:20.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}[拉里斯·斯壮] {\fs67.5}除了成为弱点 子嗣还能是什么？\N{\fs40}What are children, but a weakness?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.01,1:03:25.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愚行？\N{\fs40}A folly?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.80,1:03:28.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,徒劳？\N{\fs40}A futility?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.85,1:03:39.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,通过子女 你幻想着骗过注定胜利的大黑暗\N{\fs40}Through them, you imagine you cheat the great darkness of its victory.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.46,1:03:59.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你会永远以某种形式存在下去\N{\fs40}You will persist forever, in some form or another.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.26,1:04:05.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就好似子女会防止你化作尘土\N{\fs40}As if they will keep you from the dust.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.48,1:04:21.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但为了他们 你会交出本不该放弃的东西\N{\fs40}But for them, you surrender what you should not.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.94,1:04:27.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许你知道怎样做是对的\N{\fs40}You may know what is the right thing to be done,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.82,1:04:31.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但爱总能占据上风\N{\fs40}but love stays the hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.13,1:04:41.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,爱……\N{\fs40}Love...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.46,1:04:45.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就是失败的原因\N{\fs40}is a downfall.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.43,1:04:54.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要我说的话……最好让你的人生\N{\fs40}Best to make your way through life unencumbered...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.68,1:04:57.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没有牵绊\N{\fs40}if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.65,1:05:01.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们死了\N{\fs40}They're dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.02,1:05:04.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您一定听说过赫伦堡的故事吧 陛下\N{\fs40}You've heard the stories of Harrenhal, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.74,1:05:08.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,它以黑心赫伦的傲慢筑就\N{\fs40}It was built in hubris by Harren the Black
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.86,1:05:11.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用以纪念他自己的伟大\N{\fs40}as a monument to his own greatness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.32,1:05:14.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,筑城的泥灰中混杂着鲜血\N{\fs40}Blood mixed into the mortar.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.54,1:05:18.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,据说赫伦堡受到了诅咒\N{\fs40}It is said to be a cursed place.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.62,1:05:23.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,它会审判每一个从大门通过的人\N{\fs40}That it passes judgment on all who pass beneath its gates.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.50,1:05:25.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是你——\N{\fs40}You--
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.21,1:05:27.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作出审判的是你\N{\fs40}You passed judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.84,1:05:30.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后许下了愿望\N{\fs40}The Queen makes a wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.14,1:05:35.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王国的哪个仆人不会尽力实现它呢？\N{\fs40}What servant of the realm would not strive to fulfill it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.77,1:05:41.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想您现在会给您的父亲写信了吧？\N{\fs40}I assume you will write to your father now?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.36,1:05:44.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,拉里斯……\N{\fs40}Larys...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.52,1:05:47.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没想把事情搞成这样\N{\fs40}I did not wish for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.99,1:05:53.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很肯定 等时机成熟了……\N{\fs40}I feel certain you will reward me...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.66,1:05:57.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您会奖赏我的\N{\fs40}when the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:12.70,Open-event,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\fs65\b1\pos(957.904,251.393)}瓦雷利亚末日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:21.02,Open-event,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\b1\pos(972.571,319.393)}坦格利安家族征服维斯特洛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:13.50,Open-event,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\b1\pos(972.571,700)}瓦列利安家族参加王室婚礼
Comment: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:51.00,Open-Velaryon,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\b1\pos(1212.667,265.984)}科利斯·瓦列利安\N{\fs40\b0}“海蛇”“潮汛之主”
